25:11.426 --> 25:14.513
And I... I do think that
we're just starting to understand

25:14.638 --> 25:18.225
the impact that technology can have
on all parts of our life.

25:18.475 --> 25:19.351
Amazing.

25:19.726 --> 25:21.561
- So, you are a doctor?
