25:21.728 --> 25:24.064
And inventor, and investor.

25:24.314 --> 25:26.608
- You've served on boards of companies.

25:27.192 --> 25:29.361
I mean, why are you also a professor?

25:29.903 --> 25:34.991
Because, honestly, Standford is
the most exciting place to be right now.

25:35.075 --> 25:40.163
