25:44.960 --> 25:46.920
- The Millennials?

25:47.045 --> 25:50.006
You grew up with computers,
you're not scared of what they can do,

25:50.173 --> 25:53.635
but you still have to remember,
there's a lot that we don't know

25:53.718 --> 25:57.681
and you... you are the ones
who are gonna find out.

26:07.399 --> 26:09.359
- Professor Robertson?
- Oh, god, it's you.

26:09.442 --> 26:12.195
No, no, I can't let you in.

26:12.904 --> 26:15.490
It is a graduate level
research group

26:15.657 --> 26:16.700
and you are a freshmen?

26:16.783 --> 26:18.201
- Right. I know.
- So you're not ready.

26:18.827 --> 26:21.496
- I know, but I... I was thinking that...
- Why do want to be in a graduate group?

26:21.580 --> 26:25.125
